Class DbScenario

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hpi.bpt.chimera.database.DbObject
      • de.hpi.bpt.chimera.database.DbScenario

  • public class DbScenario
extends DbObject
    This class represents the ScenarioData in the database. It provides the functionality to retrieve all existing scenarios as well as their name.
